Population Data for Dhaka, Bangladesh

Source: R/data.R
popBGD.Rd

Grid-based population of Dhaka, Bangladesh

popBGD

Format

A data frame with four variables:

psu

primary sampling unit (PSU) ID

zone

survey enumeration area

type

slum (1) or non-slum (2)

pop

population

Examples

popBGD

#> # A tibble: 641 x 4
